author: Rei Takver
description:
Reform UK leader and figurehead Nigel Farage hasn’t been alone in basking in the media spotlight of late. Farage has been accompanied by his party chair, Zia Yusuf, a multi-millionaire tech entrepreneur who has helped to orchestrate Reform’s explosive rise. Yusuf has overseen the party’s growth to over 200,000 members and 400 regional branches since […]

The post Zia Yusuf Wants to be the UK’s Elon Musk appeared first on DeSmog.
title: Zia Yusuf Wants to be the UK’s Elon Musk
